Package: CNViz
Type: Package
Title: Copy Number Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Rebecca", "Greenblatt", email = "rebecca.greenblatt@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: CNViz takes probe, gene, and segment-level log2 copy number ratios and helps you to visualize your sample's copy number profile. You can also integrate loss of heterozygosity (LOH) and single nucleotide variant (SNV) data. 
Depends:
    R (>= 4.03),
    shiny (>= 1.5.0),
    plotly (>= 4.9.3),
Imports:
    dplyr,
    cBioPortalData,
    DT,
    magick,
    karyoploteR,
    CopyNumberPlots,
    GenomicRanges
